{"tid":153433,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［公園雙屍］  雨後公園漫步  大馬華裔夫婦同遭雷劈死  (明報）","createTime":"2017-03-12T14:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T14:58:19.000Z","uid":80392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"953ed2d69ac29f4f029439b86bee6905bf724137","tid":153433,"uid":80392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞今日發生罕見被雷電劈斃事故，一對華裔夫婦當場斃命。<br />\n<br />\n事發今日傍晚近6時，59歲華裔男子余文科與57歲妻子黃麗真，在雨後到蒲種山莊美樂花園（Taman Merak）的公園散步，其間天空不斷閃雷，有目擊者見到兩人遭雷電擊中，當場倒地，現場人員立即報警，惟救護員到場時，證實夫婦已明顯死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警員事後封鎖現場調查，兩人遺體被白布覆蓋，而路面的地磚亦裂開，足見雷電威力。當地傳媒報道，死者夫婦十分恩愛，近年每天風雨不改到公園散步，又引述目擊者指，事發時因天空不斷閃雷，該對夫婦見即將下雨，正準備回家，詎料遭雷劈中斃命。<br />\n<br />\n(星洲網)<br />\n<br />\nSources: 明報"},{"pid":"8d7411c23ccee2747fae13bd83af5c5eb5079703","tid":153433,"uid":80392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:44:23.000Z","msg":"好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93aff4921c429c2713da6e048d582b3266b4dd97","tid":153433,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595bead93fb82f26d1ce357b9de74c31ab370d08","tid":153433,"uid":37501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"都係做毒撚最好<br />\n唔出街最安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ed809dc2a32d9d8dd62f5db4a5fc48e02edca3","tid":153433,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:55:02.000Z","msg":"中左雷之黎比係你會同老婆講咩？"},{"pid":"96ecd5916f2c15b22652d9ea4764658220339cba","tid":153433,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:56:26.000Z","msg":"唔差呀<br />\n<br />\n可以同年同月同日同秒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bbd123f45d56f7a2a31980d69505d53eb816e16","tid":153433,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T14:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔差呀<br />\n<br />\n可以同年同月同日同秒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無病無痛<br />\n直情係幸運的死<br />\n諗起濟公"}]}